# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#  1729-SWMM5-Models — .gitignore
#  Keeps large, regenerable SWMM5 binary outputs ON DISK but OUT
#  of git history, so the repo stays small. Re-running a model
#  recreates these files.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# SWMM5 binary results files (~8.8 GB across the repo) — regenerable
*.out
*.OUT

# Hot-start / routing interface files (binary, regenerable)
*.hsf
*.HSF
*.rdii
*.RDII

# Scratch / temp run artifacts
*.tmp
~*

# OS / editor cruft
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
